'''''Beledeen II''''' was a [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] warship assigned to [[General/Legends|General]] [[Garm Bel Iblis/Legends|Garm Bel Iblis]] in [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]], as part of a task force for a data raid on [[Yaga Minor/Legends|Yaga Minor]]. The vessel was one of the last warships that were dispatched by [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Gial Ackbar/Legends|Ackbar]] in preparation for the major operation. The ''Beledeen II'' participated in the [[Battle of Yaga Minor (Galactic Civil War)|Battle of Yaga Minor]].

